:INFO
Sanitize Everything
Dissolve one campden tablet or use a no-rinse sanitizer (like Star San) on every piece \
of equipment: fermenter, airlock, spoon, funnel. Any wild bacteria or yeast in your \
equipment will compete with your mead yeast and produce off-flavors. Sanitation is

